{"tid":250983,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇師兄可以一齊玩天龍八部","createTime":"2017-05-20T14:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T22:51:46.000Z","uid":38675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c734520aac1bc9e70e42a672b5bfb1cdf5ac7393","tid":250983,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:03:20.000Z","msg":"好想重玩但入到去好似死城咁<br />\n上次入一個ser 見到得翻4個ac玩<br />\n嗰4個人仲要係同一個人嚟<br />\n見到條友4個ac都係6石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人可以同我一齊玩?<br />\n洛陽西邊條商街可以一條友都冇<br />\n但大陸服啲人唔多理新手<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他服可以玩?"},{"pid":"0a0d2375463fafb36e0bb9aa93f9cb9abba54b53","tid":250983,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:04:57.000Z","msg":"啱啱諗住玩私服<br />\n點知連個server都係虧嘅.."},{"pid":"6b5c0f3dc9ea17655524c22dd424c287f3ac19d7","tid":250983,"uid":85116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:08:45.000Z","msg":"我都想玩私服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 課少少無所謂,但係唔好親友團,屌佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a60d3fc3dca74ace2820ebc22752c0f1ccb90a","tid":250983,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:12:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想玩私服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 課少少無所謂,但係唔好親友團,屌佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱啱上網見到有馬來西亞服<br />\n<br />\n有冇師兄一齊?"},{"pid":"16efc2127143cf6cbe4a73b6f8a736e908c334c6","tid":250983,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:19:36.000Z","msg":"我又係前幾日想重玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點知隻game無人玩"},{"pid":"afbbce815b5111f777706a0790daa898c3fe6d6f","tid":250983,"uid":23552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:22:17.000Z","msg":"明教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78afc6f46143bfc778901ccd2143099e3273c45e","tid":250983,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:26:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我又係前幾日想重玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點知隻game無人玩</blockquote><br />\n屌 馬拉服都係入唔到<br />\n好似要轉IP先玩到<br />\n一入game即刻彈<br />\n<br />\n屌 好想玩啊宜家"},{"pid":"f471f47a9dd7b7964f797aaae2b62b29e966c9d1","tid":250983,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:26:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明教好玩 低石都可以好勁.<br />\n但係打怪好辛苦"},{"pid":"720ad6ef9d7c7bb8c65241def0278cc6b4de8508","tid":250983,"uid":42296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:30:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f56d8f1a4a9412d0fd694859b480637856e26dd","tid":250983,"uid":18222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:31:28.000Z","msg":"天山同逍遙先屈"},{"pid":"d4e4140413f7d8414481cfec137515f5f99e5f25","tid":250983,"uid":114779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:31:57.000Z","msg":"出左手機版"},{"pid":"cd495283568bbd3fecd87bde5894e6d06d5d7e0e","tid":250983,"uid":25582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:33:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出左手機版</blockquote><br />\n好唔好玩"},{"pid":"9e26c3da7ac56529d44a3a768fd2d1e51305a3eb","tid":250983,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出左手機版</blockquote><br />\n好唔好玩</blockquote><br />\n玩左5分鐘即刻刪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人認為電腦好玩啲"},{"pid":"09892bab9c1d24bc0b1c448573c02f56a2d72ca5","tid":250983,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:42:21.000Z","msg":"有冇人一齊玩..<br />\n想玩台服但要台灣電話<br />\n好麻煩"},{"pid":"c20fe57f380186366cce27e16d4912f8c66ebe18","tid":250983,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:43:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a96b58d3f7ea18c58006e1186bd18ea971859edc","tid":250983,"uid":85116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"不過ONLINE GAME都係要多人先好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538b2ed86440a8868f7319ab64ba6b6a50986773","tid":250983,"uid":18222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:49:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人一齊玩..<br />\n想玩台服但要台灣電話<br />\n好麻煩</blockquote><br />\n台服多唔多人玩先"},{"pid":"62d8da588563f8d47d02bebbecfb11fc6bfe8b9c","tid":250983,"uid":18222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:49:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>天山同逍遙先屈</blockquote><br />\n依家唔係唐門最勁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太耐無玩 唔知道有呢個門派"},{"pid":"729771895240a103f4b1555aa1e6a4d1a8ce9ddd","tid":250983,"uid":117752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:53:13.000Z","msg":"好耐之前玩過逍遙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe964ad288e20245d38335c30abc0e2ae306a61","tid":250983,"uid":25582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T15:16:45.000Z","msg":"5石逍 5石天山 5石武當留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  永遠都唔係最好打果批 但又有d用咁<br />\n天山同逍真係好好玩 以前隻逍低石果陣玩跳射好狗<br />\n以前打比武都有排打 真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知以前一齊玩果班人依家過得好唔好<br />\n入面好多好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到國服全4逍都無癮玩 無晒feel"},{"pid":"e259c11bb42b2035179fbcc74c973b24b86c44bb","tid":250983,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T02:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人一齊玩..<br />\n想玩台服但要台灣電話<br />\n好麻煩</blockquote><br />\n台服多唔多人玩先</blockquote><br />\n唔清楚<br />\nGane都入唔到<br />\n因為要係台灣到打電話過去"},{"pid":"c36a8d51ac1c8a3410adae9b030fd0c878423ef4","tid":250983,"uid":45275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"天ser EC"},{"pid":"d4c461da8dd302bfc12aa22e81446714a7a7dfad","tid":250983,"uid":14935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:48:26.000Z","msg":"玩手機版啦"},{"pid":"42c712480b70590bac0aaa297be4c683758dae99","tid":250983,"uid":7708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T18:35:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5石逍 5石天山 5石武當留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  永遠都唔係最好打果批 但又有d用咁<br />\n天山同逍真係好好玩 以前隻逍低石果陣玩跳射好狗<br />\n以前打比武都有排打 真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知以前一齊玩果班人依家過得好唔好<br />\n入面好多好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到國服全4逍都無癮玩 無晒feel</blockquote><br />\n正呀，舊時最鍾意用天山同個好朋友逍遙玩校場。呢兩個門派對碰會出現最多變化，玩左近萬場校場都唔會重複，每一次切磋都有驚喜<br />\n<br />\n利申逍ser"},{"pid":"9823e8c6d3b782f595ab22609a2a7c7bc0a01a1f","tid":250983,"uid":55408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T19:23:40.000Z","msg":"留個名先<br />\n夠多人一齊玩先join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e69bbb3b122bd0ee7e79511ab4e1c44307fa62","tid":250983,"uid":16650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T20:19:07.000Z","msg":"玩強國服都唔錯既<br />\n但一定要幾百蚊入場費<br />\n因為冇石好難玩，加上唔打得少人組你刷野"},{"pid":"b80838aaa949a36f6f9708dde1da3d07bd170be6","tid":250983,"uid":4804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T21:04:04.000Z","msg":"留個名"},{"pid":"0f1f5c0354e3802f8d5a7004cfc95be3d3be5c34","tid":250983,"uid":86762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T21:12:57.000Z","msg":"回憶<br />\n105 全3帶4天山 天ser留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得個陣淨係洗咗幾百蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外私服多人玩咩<br />\n組個隊刷小漂 都唔知要等幾耐"},{"pid":"10a881bd48a34816114feecc30222b823c989433","tid":250983,"uid":101522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T21:26:22.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"13a2045cf94d4eff0c566f777a615d7f1b8e0170","tid":250983,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:08:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩強國服都唔錯既<br />\n但一定要幾百蚊入場費<br />\n因為冇石好難玩，加上唔打得少人組你刷野</blockquote><br />\n就係呢下先嬲<br />\n刷40符都要好似查你家宅咁"},{"pid":"35c2572d0bdf4f6e86e246114fedeedbe2f701a4","tid":250983,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回憶<br />\n105 全3帶4天山 天ser留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得個陣淨係洗咗幾百蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外私服多人玩咩<br />\n組個隊刷小漂 都唔知要等幾耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我近排玩緊個私服叫 幻羽天龍<br />\n<br />\n但係入面啲人好戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你出去刷野會俾惡人谷啲人係咁殺<br />\n<br />\n明明已經唔係刷重樓嘅野都會清你<br />\n<br />\n想靜靜地刷啲贈點卷都會開gps即刻去搵你再殺你<br />\n<br />\n佢哋痴線到係主城都清你<br />\n<br />\n個個都8,9石 根本你唔係一開Ser就玩嗰啲人就會俾人清算"},{"pid":"82cf0a5436684550e5e207772ed42b568fac174d","tid":250983,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:15:16.000Z","msg":"有冇私服玩"},{"pid":"bb5302db68038c01a7be2f4735ccd9855b00fc3c","tid":250983,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:16:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇私服玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有 叫幻羽天龍 不過入邊啲人痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n成埋友圍威喂<br />\n<br />\n無人夠佢哋做"},{"pid":"96bf7a795c6d39c3d35fe46e708a82ffd2723ebb","tid":250983,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:17:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇私服玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有 叫幻羽天龍 不過入邊啲人痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n成埋友圍威喂<br />\n<br />\n無人夠佢哋做</blockquote><br />\n咁唔玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ea3c1cdaad7e2531f763b6bf0ac948b1f58bc2","tid":250983,"uid":101519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:18:57.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ff05e8da4c9ccd49fe687df76f399d90ec0c2e47","tid":250983,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇私服玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有 叫幻羽天龍 不過入邊啲人痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n成埋友圍威喂<br />\n<br />\n無人夠佢哋做</blockquote><br />\n咁唔玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啊 我都想翻大陸服玩<br />\n上樂古睇過有個Ser好似多香港人玩<br />\n但一入到去又係無人理我<br />\n<br />\n同埋大陸服帳號都好似幾難申請<br />\n我之前都係要係淘寶買"},{"pid":"d62f3663527fc624e6cffd7e463ab20b8cea848d","tid":250983,"uid":64464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:21:05.000Z","msg":"師兄係咪玩呀<br />\n我都想玩返<br />\n不如開個谷加哂D人入去一齊玩啦"},{"pid":"344df827883a3c0b16ebb96010c51dd90d5f7c09","tid":250983,"uid":78117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:26:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8da4d71503ee5ee459052fdde133f8ba926a2ad","tid":250983,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:27:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>師兄係咪玩呀<br />\n我都想玩返<br />\n不如開個谷加哂D人入去一齊玩啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以嘅<br />\n多過5條友就開"},{"pid":"e090ef1f33f6480692997a8138e14a0cd49d1579","tid":250983,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天山童 夜魔天山打手留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當年成60幾70人開紅 好撚爽 <br />\n<br />\n然後去掛機隱身消刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正服你只要唔係敵幫<br />\n<br />\n生活玩家都冇人郁你<br />\n<br />\n但私服直頭係成班黑警咁見人就郁"},{"pid":"451f861658022f9ea5eee224106082cb75146e83","tid":250983,"uid":115388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:28:51.000Z","msg":"me"},{"pid":"30ae4db040b0a973fd1da0d0d1cacdea0420588a","tid":250983,"uid":100447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:33:10.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"09879d5cc910e7e2c621647330a4d1da287963b4","tid":250983,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩強國服都唔錯既<br />\n但一定要幾百蚊入場費<br />\n因為冇石好難玩，加上唔打得少人組你刷野</blockquote><br />\n幾百蚊夠咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢隻game入場費唔係幾皮野咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77add070f56c56768a8086066a9e9cbb0838c85","tid":250983,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:35:33.000Z","msg":"之前樂古有個大陸服要入game 刷喇叭先有人搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4557aecac64df2e2f645f1752f2c7a3dfa3c362b","tid":250983,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:37:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>天山童 夜魔天山打手留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當年成60幾70人開紅 好撚爽 <br />\n<br />\n然後去掛機隱身消刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正服你只要唔係敵幫<br />\n<br />\n生活玩家都冇人郁你<br />\n<br />\n但私服直頭係成班黑警咁見人就郁</blockquote><br />\n好正常,天龍咁多私服,除返開每個都唔多人玩,反正到最後人流都會消散晒,緊係執笠前盡量屠得幾多就幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832cd80a18cb0383eef7566259139db73c98fae2","tid":250983,"uid":20182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:39:20.000Z","msg":"明教出左45技個陣打交好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c465a470807ba454f1f2e359dbcb327fa4ac54d2","tid":250983,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:39:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockqu