citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:26:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩左兩年都係唔識打校場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日掛機刷副本已經好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打交我都唔叻<br />\n刷副本都夠我現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b2fa71016fab40b81a9d7b4eed77ec9f746e24","tid":250983,"uid":24589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:40:12.000Z","msg":"初中雞果時既事啦 <br />\n天山童ser<br />\n果陣揀左天龍 無課玩到90幾lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾內外攻半桶水 連師門任單推都差D死<br />\n結果我全加血當半個少林算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到後期玩屬性 天龍先叫冇咁垃圾<br />\n不過果陣都冇玩啦<br />\n無課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好記得果陣個個禮拜六公會跑商<br />\n有一期有外掛 我掛低lv場掛一晚都升到1lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想搵返果陣既partner 傲少天 丫璃 吊兒郎當"},{"pid":"f2f8bcb81e251f534f4b2c0ede91ef46c6181665","tid":250983,"uid":52210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:57:11.000Z","msg":"記得岩岩玩個時仲係套裝時代<br />\n個陣武當最勁<br />\n之後D人發現逍遙屈機<br />\n玩逍遙即刻變左做熱潮<br />\n近攻好似天山之外都唔勁<br />\n少林更加係狗也不屌<br />\n<br />\n出左45技之後 <br />\n唔記得係咪45 不過黑衣個招係飛去人地個到<br />\n明教好似仲屈<br />\n之後又平衡番D<br />\n不過少林星宿都仲係少數<br />\n<br />\n之後慢慢屬性攻變左做主力<br />\n星宿都開始多番人玩<br />\n<br />\n主流副本一直都係峨嵋同逍遙<br />\n<br />\n募容岩岩出個陣我都玩到90lv<br />\n係幾勁<br />\n之後就冇掂到lu<br />\n<br />\n其實我講左咁多<br />\n只係想問下少林係咪都仲係狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a979ca6b575ce18a8676f6d96addfe97d69da8cb","tid":250983,"uid":48213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:59:49.000Z","msg":"會唔會有冇人放ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想自己升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660ca60f2e0c562240e2ce35795ef57296c319a8","tid":250983,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"